dc_description_s: Relief shown by 5 feet contours, hachures, spot heights, and form lines. Shows cadastral information, township and property boundaries, quarries, overhead H.T. electricity and telegraph lines, post offices, public and private properties. Includes index diagram to adjoining sheets. Information on the number of sheet published for covering this area is unavailable. Map Collection has three. "© United Republic of Tanzania 1967".
dc_publisher_s: [Dar es Salaam] : Survey Division, Ministry of Lands Settlement and Water Development, 1967.
